Process called "check_left_recursion_recursive" that takes grammar as Grammar and current_rule as String and target as String and visited as Dictionary[String, Boolean] returns Boolean:
    Note: Recursive helper for left recursion detection
    If visited contains key current_rule:
    Return false Set visited at key current_rule to true If grammar.rules contains key current_rule:
